org.modelio.gproject.gproject.url

Class GUrlProject

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.modelio.gproject.gproject.GProject
      • org.modelio.gproject.gproject.remote.GRemoteProject
        • org.modelio.gproject.gproject.url.GUrlProject

  • public class GUrlProject
extends GRemoteProject
    Represents a project shared on a HTTP server or anything that can be accessed from an URI.

    The URI must be handled by UriConnections in order to work.
